{{Y|Press [{{W|F1}}] or [{{W|?}}] while in quick menu for help.}}

{{W|* App restart is required after approving or enabling this mod from disabled state.}}
{{w|* If you are experiencing dark color main menu after restart, as far as I'm concerned it's safe to ignore.}}
{{W|* To access quick menu screen, assign a key to quick menu in [Quick Menu] section from Key Mapping.}}
{{w|* This mod doesn't support new input manager (yet).}}

This mod adds a new menu which acts as a hub to ties all status screens into one keymap.
Main purpose is to free up some keymaps for no-numpad user or anyone who think their keymap is a mess (aka me for both cases).
